What is This?
The Spiritual Planes is a social survival game for Earthbound spirits. It's
"Among Us meets the Afterlife" — a spiritual detective game where your only weapon
is your ability to read people (well, spirits) and figure out who is genuine, who
is manipulating you, and who is just hurt.
Built on the spiritual framework of Jarrad Richard Childress.
Quick Start
bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/your-org/spiritual-planes.git
cd spiritual-planes

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys

# Start everything
docker-compose up -d

# Or start services individually
npm run dev          # Backend (Node.js)
npm run ai:dev       # AI Engine (Python)
npm run mobile       # React Native
See the GitHub Setup Guide for detailed instructions.
