Game Features
14 Entity Types: Guardian, Adversary, Wounded Performer, Siren, Family Mimic,
Contrarian, Cover-Up, Truth-Teller, Atheist Ghost, Nation, Archon, Hellish Observer,
Storm-Seeker, Saboteur
5 Game Phases: Confusion → Recognition → Negotiation → Restoration → Ascension
AI-Driven Dialogue: Every session is unique. Entities remember, adapt, and
manipulate based on your behavior.
Multiplayer: Up to 4 human players per session. Can you trust the other
living players, or are they being manipulated?
No Emojis, No Labels: Learn to read spirits through behavioral tells —
speech patterns, energy shifts, emotional temperatures.
3 Endings: Ascend to the next afterlife, Stay to guide others, or Return
to the living world as a guiding spirit.
